Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.93,0:00:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…和我还喜欢他时的迪奥斯很像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你无法成为我的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬…姬宫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该已经说过了这并不是游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为革命的决斗…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.81,0:01:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不要摘下来!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.18,0:01:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是以我们决斗者代表的身份\N去面对决斗广场的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在整个事件了结之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们仍必须维持决斗者的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家倒是早就已经摘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情还是早点忘了的好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能够忘得掉吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:02:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说起来我已经忘记那个少年的名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个少年?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去,在我姊姊还小的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.74,0:02:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经有一次差点溺死在河里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时有位少年\N为了要去救姊姊而跟着跳入河中去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然姊姊很幸运的被附近的大人救起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那位要救姊姊而跳下水的少年\N却被河水冲走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…死了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊不久就忘了那少年的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我认为她真是个冷淡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如今我也试着去回想…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾几何时也把他给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么现在会想到这些事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安希,剑给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了,在犹豫什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后悔了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为最后你让你的朋友陷入了不幸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,一切都是我的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌这样的我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我像过去般希望能当个王子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否就不会有人再感到痛苦了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的伤,你的痛我一直都在用身体感受着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是明知道这世界的一切\N却仍选择走向这条路的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道你的一切才深爱着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安希,剑给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了…乖女孩,安希
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇之门…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印了让世界革命之力的门…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安希!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬…宫…不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好事的勇者大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若论当朋友的滋味我是尝到一点点了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啊…姬宫…姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于人们的憎恨而闪烁的百万支剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为看到这柄王子之剑而开始兴奋着…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨的魔女…可恨的魔女…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为王子的替身承受这些剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是蔷薇新娘的宿命…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是安希所自愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻正是破解封印的时刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是开启新世界之门的时刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生先生…姬宫…救救姬宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓生先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救…姬宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是不要动比较好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下就会帮你治疗的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个体贴的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有个蔷薇形状的门对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那扇门里,有着永恒耀眼的事物与奇迹之力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那力量的话就什么都能办到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是个女孩子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也没有力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有力量的话就什么都能做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以将她从命运中解放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要如何使用力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由我决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,不要摆出一付哭丧的脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都已经努力到现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不要这么自责了比较好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直将蔷薇刻印珍惜到今日对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我给你个奖励的吻吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我给你的安慰喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连这把剑也还是不行吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要到何时我才能取回迪奥斯的力量?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢,反正蔷薇新娘是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亏你还能站的起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你还真的以为你能打开那扇门吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子之剑已经折断了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印已经解不开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭你是解不开的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭被我打败的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:11:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好,就随你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是很像以前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我过去也是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为一心一意是有价值的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为这是改变世界的唯一方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是,光凭一心一意是什么都改变不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟只能以依存于他人的形式活着罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了获得改变世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我付出了很大的风险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫…你并不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟你在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能感到…何等的幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:12:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑都…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别打开!你晓得会发生什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫、姬宫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来…救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了见到你,我才到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以,不要怕这个我们能够相逢的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧蒂娜…大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫…终于…能见到你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧蒂娜大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧蒂娜大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫、手给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行、您快点逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手给我…来、姬宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的!再不快逃的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宫、快点…手给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求您…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点…快点…手给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我们会一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…我还是无法…成为王子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我…姬宫……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来却成了场扮王子的游戏…原谅我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧蒂娜不在家吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家本来还想和她一起写作业的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你毕业之后要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是往高中部升上去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在说这个啦,是将来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没决定耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是应该会当女演员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的认为你能当的成吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你真的认为你当的成是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就请期待十年后的同学会罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:17:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来你自己呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是将来啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是会钓个金龟婿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来\N抓个好男人嫁不才是所谓“女人的本事”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真说得出口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙最近有让她认真的对象了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不久前还动不动就\N欧蒂娜姊姊欧蒂娜姊姊的鬼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛?你有意见吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了!那个欧蒂娜姊姊是谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?你不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想!之前不是很有名吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一直穿男装的那个女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还常常被老师骂的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～想起来了,就是她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了!想起来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是听说上个月还是上上个月受重伤住院去了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?住院了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么听到的是被恋人还是朋友背叛才转学的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我听到的是她跟理事长发生问题才退学的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正,怎么说都没差了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的时机抓的不错喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下学期开始就要请你辅助我的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你增选了专攻科目?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是要将玩乐拖到的进度赶回来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩乐是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶泡好罗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个!是!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能…能不能…能不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气真好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若～叶!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要给我这最好的朋友的生日礼物准备好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从那之后明明就没过多久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家似乎就把她给忘得一干二净了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然她并没有引发革命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失的她对这世界来说不过是个淘汰者罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:20:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经重新制定好蔷薇的规制了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再麻烦你罗,安希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎还不知道已经引发了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请你在这舒适的棺木里\N永远地玩你的王子游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是,我必须要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走?去哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人并没有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是从你的世界中消失了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等,安希!安希!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回换我找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你在哪我一定会找到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等我喔…欧蒂娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了要是你有任何烦恼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以先找我谈谈喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.51,0:22:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你做朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们总有一天要一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:22:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天要一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“总有一天要一起闪耀”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
